rows.label: qst103608_msg0002
rows.name: The ship... Has it already sailed?

rows.label: qst103608_msg0003
rows.name:
Yes... I'm afraid
Senator Stole got away.

rows.label: qst103608_msg0004
rows.name:
Some of his allies had concealed
themselves on the ship.

rows.label: qst103608_msg0005
rows.name:
The attack by Brionac must
have just been a ruse so that
the senator could escape...

rows.label: qst103608_msg0008
rows.name: Then we should head for Fons Maim.

rows.label: qst103608_msg0009
rows.name: We'll chase him to the ends of Alst!

rows.label: qst103608_msg0010
rows.name:
I'll report this incident
to my superiors!
